 it's heartbreaking how all the good stuff

1:47:31.180 --> 1:47:32.540
 is getting politicized.

1:47:32.540 --> 1:47:34.240
 Yeah, that's right, and it shouldn't be,

1:47:34.240 --> 1:47:36.580
 and it'll seem less political.

