 I'm confident because I'm an optimist

1:48:11.740 --> 1:48:12.780
 that we will get through this

1:48:12.780 --> 1:48:15.300
 and we will be better at sustaining our environment

1:48:15.300 --> 1:48:16.700
 in future decades.

